content.rendered:
Precision engineered from 6061 billet Alumnimum.

Polished and brushed Aluminium finish.

Anodised finish for corrosion protection.

120mm Diameter.

Designed for use with soft shackles and synthetic winch ropes.

WLL: 12,500 kg / 27,557 lbs

Destructive Test Break Load: 62,508 kg / 137,806 lbs

Australian designed, engineered and tested

Backed by a comprehensive Quality Assurance Program, each ring is individually x-rayed for inclusions.
